":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"刪除佢學藉等佢返上去就最好 !!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"返左去深圳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b6cb3ca6768a3a1082166db7e4914beec5fc5f","tid":1702980,"uid":17232,"like":28,"dislike":8,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"港科大全體教職員工，同學們，校友們：<br />\n<br />\n關於在本月6日公開論壇會上發生的事件，其中包括我們科大的學生被襲擊事件，我們想和大家表達如下幾點：<br />\n<br />\n1.我們在事後看到多份關於整個事件的現場視頻，其中包含對蓄意襲擊和毆打學生事件我們完全無法接受。我們向大家保證，我們不能容忍任何校園暴力，對襲擊事件強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.懲戒惡意滋事學生和同夥是我們當前最緊迫的要務之一。我們正在尋求專業的協助更有效的調查所有掌握的影像資料，徵集現場目擊者，尋找施暴者及蓄意掩護的同夥，同時設法證實其中有誰是港科大學生。在我們盡最大努力的同時，希望大家也能夠協助我們，盡快找到施暴者。</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 一旦查實施暴者及其同夥，如果是本校學生，我們將按照校規追責和嚴重懲罰，不論本校或校外人士，我們會追究其法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n4.部分科大師生表達了對論壇會當天安保措施的疑問。我們會對當天的安保措施，以及事發後現場保安處理襲擊事件的過程做全面的檢討。<br />\n<br />\n讓我們肩並肩，共同維護校園的安全與和諧。"},{"pid":"4da9ae280e502a2baeb35af104542d04e8627ab8","tid":1702980,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d6fba2de132a59a33332d3655572c478bf6fbf12","tid":1702980,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3bc516ae4f7d841a006667e2c6ddfb8e9212a1","tid":1702980,"uid":146030,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"史維狗"},{"pid":"a0774a826bcb7af74f4602bbe6c8c13a93a1f5d6","tid":1702980,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4fc353b17eae7350926da79ede1406c40dfb8b","tid":1702980,"uid":291167,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"要追究就先追究首先無故打人嘅大陸生，校長唔好當佢哋好無辜咁，亦都唔好將被告變原告，姑息咗呢班頭腦亢奮嘅大陸人"},{"pid":"c3930ba4cbb83f7795076a3f1a5b5d838f05ba40","tid":1702980,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5eed37651242cfd787e6f5527615bf97a4f24ec","tid":1702980,"uid":36121,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔使吹奏科大喇<br />\n屎維到宜家都唔敢condemn班曱甴 但已經連續出幾次信condemn local學生<br />\n佢個公開portal第一件查嘅事唔係周同學呀 係forum鶳支那仔事件呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於推人嗰件支那狗呢？<br />\n潑奶茶落local嗰件支那狗呢？<br />\nLG7嗰7單NDS襲擊事件呢？<br />\n性非禮local學生嗰件支那教授呢？<br />\n再加上意圖DQ民選校董 唔俾兩屆學生校董上台<br />\n學校到底有邊次維護過local嘅權利？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本喺科大 NDS就係迷你版POPO 做乜都唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前周同學入院嗰陣佢死都唔做嘢 宜家周同學嘅死引起民憤 佢先逼住被表態咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而你班連登仔唔知頭唔知路 居然走去吹奏佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cefc3f03d968ed05964b139f3f79c733c20e872a","tid":1702980,"uid":997,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:59:39.000Z","msg":"交晒d支那人名上去"},{"pid":"3bfaf8f06b7b0e05ccaa936e761887a9e5ed2484","tid":1702980,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f3b79104253e5a82efc430a9c6fd3820343b22","tid":1702980,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:02:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>想多啲人參與唔同行動？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>要記住嚟場革命唔係淨係屬於連登仔<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地多數只會認同大眾都吹奏緊既野</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地有咩可以做？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1）我地要多啲係唔同post下面<span style=\"color: red;\">瘋狂洗版行動文宣</span>同發夢注意事項post<br />\n2）仲有要<span style=\"color: red;\">係街不斷airdrop啲文宣俾人<br />\n</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3）隨身袋住啲文宣周街貼</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">頭兩項都係零成本 <br />\n你唔係唔做呀嘛</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"020561bef50b27dad8d686762b0589d867354c87","tid":1702980,"uid":1544,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"external professional 咪即係警犬<br />\n屎維我屌你老母"},{"pid":"175702b5f19573a8999aae1759e2b852df606201","tid":1702980,"uid":335834,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"收到風私了人嗰個休班警黎 校長譴責未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ab63738f4be609f4dd2bb220b486abf118f756","tid":1702980,"uid":47548,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"edc72d7cf1886d16b8d5b5ff0d4cb9a695aa15f7","tid":1702980,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"020561bef50b27dad8d686762b0589d867354c87","tid":1702980,"uid":1544,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"external professional 咪即係警犬<br />\n屎維我屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"咪就撚係"},{"pid":"992d32716401786e560efd227c7ce939cf2d003e","tid":1702980,"uid":302382,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"非禮人嗰個教授點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2629865329d7e153027daf790f566efa8099a8","tid":1702980,"uid":74155,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"28ab63738f4be609f4dd2bb220b486abf118f756","tid":1702980,"uid":47548,"like":4,"dis